WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.966 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.966 --> 00:00:03.381 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:03.381 --> 00:00:10.640 align:middle line:90%


00:00:10.640 --> 00:00:14.374 align:middle line:84%
>> Asking the question, do you
believe in life after life?

00:00:14.374 --> 00:00:16.740 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh my.

00:00:16.740 --> 00:00:19.710 align:middle line:84%
