00:29:15.818 --> 00:29:17.610 align:middle line:84%
>> I guess I won't be
seeing him in heaven.

00:29:17.610 --> 00:29:18.900 align:middle line:90%
That's where I'm going.

00:29:18.900 --> 00:29:20.840 align:middle line:84%
So yeah, that's what
I think happens.

