You do go to heaven or hell,
just depending on, I guess,

00:29:25.140 --> 00:29:26.340 align:middle line:90%
what you did through life.

00:29:26.340 --> 00:29:28.950 align:middle line:84%
So I guess I subscribe to
the Christian point of view.

00:29:28.950 --> 00:29:32.310 align:middle line:90%


00:29:32.310 --> 00:29:34.610 align:middle line:84%
>> I think about
the finality of it,

00:29:34.610 --> 00:29:39.180 align:middle line:84%
and I think about that I
don't want to think about it.

00:29:39.180 --> 00:29:41.415 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I think
when people die,

00:29:41.415 --> 00:29:44.470 align:middle line:84%
it's just like
candle is blowed out.

00:29:44.470 --> 00:29:48.030 align:middle line:84%
