That's my thought.

00:29:50.880 --> 00:29:53.262 align:middle line:84%
>> I guess either you
go to heaven or hell.

00:29:53.262 --> 00:29:54.720 align:middle line:84%
What you do here
on Earth is what's

00:29:54.720 --> 00:29:57.480 align:middle line:84%
going to happen to
