>> So you just saw the tunnel?

00:30:18.630 --> 00:30:18.895 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:30:18.895 --> 00:30:20.010 align:middle line:90%
And I just never made it.

00:30:20.010 --> 00:30:21.510 align:middle line:90%
>> Ah.

00:30:21.510 --> 00:30:23.000 align:middle line:90%
>> Just woke up.

00:30:23.000 --> 00:30:24.420 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

